Package: aircrack-ng
Version: 1.7
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: root-repo
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, make, automake, autoconf, libc++, libnl, libpcap, libsqlite, openssl, pcre, zlib, iw, ethtool, libtool, usbutils
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://www.aircrack-ng.org/
Description: Wireless network security auditing suite
 aircrack-ng is a complete suite of tools for assessing WiFi network
 security. It captures and analyzes packets, performs attacks,
 and cracks WEP/WPA/WPA2 keys. Includes monitoring, injection,
 and cracking tools.
